<i>noun</i>: 아비규환 [아비규환] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>아비규환 [아비규환]</dt><br>
<dd>agonizing cries; appalling confusion; inferno</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 여러 사람이 처참하고 혼란스러운 상황에 빠져 울부짖고 몸부림치는 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The state in which many people fall into a very cruel, chaotic situation where they cry and struggle.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>